Hello everyone, I hope you can help me fix this so I can land on Mars for the first time!

Reproduction Step:

Use this spacecraft (Attached below), go to orbit, and rendezvous with Mars.

Time-warping to Mars' SoI Entry and the bugs kicks in (Not responding, unable to do anything, even took me 5 minutes after pressed the Power button).

Files:

Craft file

Log file

Edited December 10, 2018 by illusionist

Since your game is not up to date, your mods do not have to be up to date. Find the correct versions, redownload and try again.

Also, try manual installing, CKAN messes with mod installs.

Hey Xd the great (sorry I don't know to respond your answer),

I love this version, it is so far the most compatible with mods I already have and with my save file. I'm not sure if they works in future version.

Please tell me. Thanks!

Simply enough:

Spoiler 

NullReferenceException: Object reference not set to an instance of an object
  at PhysicsRangeExtender.TerrainExtender.ExtendTerrainDistance () [0x00000] in <filename unknown>:0 
  at PhysicsRangeExtender.TerrainExtender.Apply () [0x00000] in <filename unknown>:0 
  at PhysicsRangeExtender.TerrainExtender.LateUpdate () [0x00000] in <filename unknown>:0

Your log is full of them. So, remove Physics Range Extender and try again.
